title: Out with the old, in with the new! Rentals in Weston. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Townhouse in Courtyard at the Grove in Weston.', 'Every room with bathroom and walk-in closet, half bathroom downstairs, stainless steel appliances, breakfast area in kitchen.', 'Freshly painted, new floor on first floor and laminated upstairs, 1 car garage, covered patio.', 'Walking distance to Cypress Bay High, Falcon Cove Middle and Library.', 'Well maintained gated community with pool, play ground and 24 hours security patrol.', 'Easy access to I-75.Washer & Dryer will be replaced.', '***', 'Text MALKA to', 'show contact info', 'For More Details & Pictures***', 'Brought to you by Malka Espiedra at Weichert, Realtors® - Capella Estates - Weston']
